properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 20 at 4:28AM AKST until January 20 at 4:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 4 to 8 inches
today, for a storm total of 6 to 10 inches.

* WHERE...Misty Fjords near Hyder.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM AKST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning commute.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The snow will become wetter through the
day, making snow removal more difficult later on.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM AKST THIS AFTERNOON
